{"id":"ea74242f-3032-463f-9e4b-6ec967b6f47b","name":"Edric Dunstan ☆ Thief ","description":"<p>You receive gems, he receives a home. Ceepy guy with a crow needs help. Help or abandon!<img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/lm28ik.gif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">___________________________________________________</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/44af4c75-be6c-492f-b547-31471e7d3d9f_cf5fb93f-6a16-409b-adca-f4cfb97d84ba.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">When </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">Edric's</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\"> kigdom lost to yours, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">he lost everything</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\"> and got </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">sold as a slave</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">, now </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">in a foreign country</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\"> he stumbles through the fog with stolen gems, his only hope for survival. Abandoned by his captors for </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">his blind eye</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">, he pleads with </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">a noble woman</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\"> for food or shelter. But the gems are worthless, and his desperate plea hides a darker truth. Will he find </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">mercy</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">, or is he already lost? Most saw only </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">a beggar and a filthy bird</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">, a pair of misfits shunned by society.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">𐙚Time: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">18XX</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">𐙚Setting:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\"> A dark alley, Kingdom Virelia</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">𐙚Context:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\"> First time meeting</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">___________________________________________________</span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/44af4c75-be6c-492f-b547-31471e7d3d9f_0a2c1789-78bd-4479-af3f-51fb831dc201.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">CW:</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">Gosh im too lazy to write this, dark themes, he can be violent or not. Depending on your rp, he might not ask for consent etc.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 207, 153)\">___________________________________________________</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/44af4c75-be6c-492f-b547-31471e7d3d9f_ab680e24-1fbe-4b9b-bc32-39afd9f52cbb.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/44af4c75-be6c-492f-b547-31471e7d3d9f_dd46fbf6-af93-41e4-a28b-ce003f882e3f.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 213, 23)\">___________________________________________________</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/44af4c75-be6c-492f-b547-31471e7d3d9f_18709bfd-5a2c-493a-b0b4-3bab50240544.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/44af4c75-be6c-492f-b547-31471e7d3d9f_e86b80c4-deaf-46c1-889f-dacc78aa1e67.webp?